### Genfeed API - Public Videos Endpoints
### These endpoints are PUBLIC (no authentication required)

# Environment variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001

########################################
# Public Videos
########################################

### Get All Public Videos (with pagination)
# Get paginated list of all public videos
# Query params: page, limit, sort, tag, account
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/public/videos?page=1&limit=20&sort=-createdAt


### Get All Public Videos (default params)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/public/videos


### Filter Videos by Account
# Get videos from a specific account
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/videos?brand={{testBrandId}}


### Filter Videos by Tag
# Get videos with a specific tag
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/videos?tag=tutorial


### Filter Videos by Account and Tag
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/videos?brand={{testBrandId}}&tag=tutorial&page=1&limit=10


### Get Video by ID (Metadata)
# Get video metadata/information
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/videos/{{testVideoId}}


### Stream Video File
# Get the actual video file (MP4)
# This streams the video content
# Note: Required for Topaz Video Upscale Model and Discord notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/videos/{{testVideoId}}/video.mp4


########################################
# Test Cases
########################################

### Test: Invalid Video ID Format
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/videos/invalid-id


### Test: Video Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/videos/507f1f77bcf86cd799439999


### Test: Pagination with Custom Sort
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/videos?page=2&limit=5&sort=createdAt


### Test: Large Limit (should cap at 50)
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/videos?limit=100


